Why not :purpose???
An umbrella term for capturing data about a person or object electronically
(u / umbrella-term-777
      :op1 (p / person
            :op1-of (o2 / or
                  :op1-of (a / about
                        :mod-of (d / data-777)
                        :quant-of (e / electronic))
                  :op2 (o / object-777))))

Power source должен быть отдельным концептом в идеале, но откуда взяться источнику этого концепта?
An additional power source that can be used in the event of power failure
(p2 / possible
      :domain (u / use-01
            :ARG1 (s / source
                  :mod (p3 / power
                        :mod (a / additional)))
            :ARG2 (e / event-777
                  :ARG0-of (f / fail-01
                        :ARG1 (p / power)))))